data.title: 北京外研版七年级上册Module 1模块检测

question_boxs.description: 听对话，根据对话的内容，从下面各题所给的选项中选择最佳选项。录音听一遍。

content.contentDesc:
M: Excuse me, Grace.
W: Yes?
M: I found a computer game. Is it yours?
W: Oh, yes. Thanks!
M: You're welcome. Is that your box?
W: Yes. My ring, my watch and my ID card are in it.
M: I see. What's that?
W: It's a red bag.
M: Is that your bag?

W: No, it isn't. It is my teacher's bag.

subContents.content: The boy found a(n) _____.
The box is _____.
What is NOT in the box?
What colour is the bag?
The bag is _____.

question_boxs.description: 听独白，将表格所缺的关键信息填写在相应位置上。录音听两遍。

content.content:
NameSamLing Mei
From_____China
Favourite colour__________
GradeSeven_____
ClassFour_____
content.contentDesc: Hi, I'm Sam. I'm from England. My favourite colour is yellow. I have a friend. Her name is Ling Mei. She is from China. Her favourite colour is red. We are in Grade Seven. I'm in Class Four, but she is in Class Three.

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—What's the weather like in spring in Jinan?

—_____.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是形容词的辨析。句意：——济南春天的天气怎么样？——温暖。It's warm.温暖。cool 凉爽的；hot 热的；cold 冷的。

因此，正确答案是A。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content: Practice more, _____ you'll do better in playing chess.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是连词的用法。句意：多练习，你下棋就会下得更好。but 但是，表转折；and 和，然后；when 当……时候；after 在……之后。

因此，正确答案是B。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—Do you like _____ TV?

—No, I don't.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是固定搭配。句意：——你喜欢看电视吗？——不，我不喜欢。watch TV 看电视；like doing sth. 喜欢做某事。see 动词，看到。

因此，正确答案是C。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—_____?

—He is twelve.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是特殊疑问句的辨析。句意：——他多大了？——他12岁。A.他怎么样？B.他多大了？C.他是做什么的？D项不正确。

因此，正确答案是B。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—Where are you from?

—Lingling is from _____ and we are from _____.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是名词辨析。句意：——你们来自于哪里？——玲玲来自于中国，我们来自于英国。China 中国；England 英国；Chinese 中文，中国人；English 英语。

因此，正确答案是D。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content: Robert Brown comes from America. Robert is his _____ name and Brown is his _____ name.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是固定词组。句意：Robert Brown来自美国，Robert是他的名，Brown是他的姓。given name 名字，教名；family name 姓。

因此，正确答案是A。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content: Li Na started playing _____ tennis at the age of six. She is one of _____ best tennis players in the world.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是冠词的使用。句意：李娜在她六岁时开始打网球。她是全世界最好的网球选手之一。play tennis 表示“打网球”，tennis前不加任何冠词；最高级best之前要加定冠词the。

因此，正确答案是C。

subContents.content: You _____ a teacher. I _____ a student. My sister _____ a student, too.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是系动词的辨析。句意：你是一位老师。我是一个学生。我的妹妹也是一个学生。you与are搭配；I与am搭配；my sister是第三人称单数，与is搭配。

因此，正确答案是C。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—Are you Jim?

—_____.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是一般疑问句的肯定回答。句意：——你是Jim吗？——是的，我是。Are you Jim? 肯定回答是“Yes, I am.”；否定回答是“No, I'm not.”。

因此，正确答案是B。

question_boxs.description: 从下面各题所给选项中，选择最佳选项。

subContents.content:
—_____

—That's a good idea!

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是情景交际。句意：——去游泳怎么样？——那是个好主意。What do I do? 我该怎么办？What about going swimming? 去游泳怎么样？Are you free? 你有空吗？Where are you from? 你来自哪里？

因此，正确答案是B。

question_boxs.description: 阅读下面的短文，掌握其大意，然后从短文后各题所给的选项中，选择最佳选项。

content.content: Look at this girl. _____ name is Wang Meimei. _____ is twelve. Wang Ming is her brother. He is _____ Class Three Grade Two. Do you know how old he is? He is fourteen years old. The brother _____ sister are in No. 2 Middle School. Their mother _____ a teacher. She is an _____ teacher. Their father, Mr Wang, is a teacher, _____. He is a Chinese teacher in No. 8 Middle School. Their students all love them because they love their students. They have (有) a cat. _____ name is Mimi. _____ a nice cat. The cat and Wang Meimei are _____ friends.

analysisList.text:
此题考查的是代词的辨析。句意：她的名字是Wang Meimei。her 形容词性物主代词，她的，修饰名词。she 她，作主语；he 他，作主语；his 他的。由上句“Look at this girl.”可知是女孩，所以用her。

因此，正确答案是A。

此题考查的是人称代词的辨析。句意：她12岁。she 她；he 他；I 我；you 你/你们。由上文知道是女孩， 所以用she。

因此，正确答案是D。

此题考查的是介词的辨析。句意：他在2年级3班。在某个班级用介词in。on 在……上面；with 有；at 在（时间，地点等）。

因此，正确答案是C。

此题考查的是连词的辨析。句意：哥哥和妹妹都在第二中学。and 并且；but 但是；so 所以；or 否则。

因此，正确答案是D。

此题考查的是系动词的辨析。句意：他们的妈妈是一位老师。一般现在时，their mother作主语，be动词用is。

因此，正确答案是B。

此题考查的是形容词及名词的辨析。句意：她是一位英语老师。English 英文的；Chinese 中文的；Japanese 日语的；England 英国。某个学科的老师，所以排除D。冠词是an，所选单词第一个音素需是元音音素，所以是“English”。Chinese和Japanese前的不定冠词应用a。

因此，正确答案是A。

此题考查的是副词、数词及介词的辨析。句意：他们的爸爸，Wang先生，也是一位老师。too 副词，也，用于肯定句句末；also 副词，也；用于肯定句句中。to 介词，对于；two 数词，二。

因此，正确答案是B。

此题考查的是形容词性物主代词的正确形式。句意：它的名字是Mimi。its 形容词性物主代词，它的，修饰名词，位于句首，首字母大写。it 它；it's=it is 它是。

因此，正确答案是A。

此题考查的是代词和系动词。句意：它是一只友好的猫。it's=it is 它是；its 它的；they're 它们是；it 它，作主语或宾语。句中缺少主语和谓语，所以排除A和D。根据句意“一只猫”，所以是单数形式。

因此，正确答案是C。

此题考查的是形容词的辨析。句意：猫和Wang Meimei是好朋友。good 好的；right 对的；fine 美好的，晴朗的，健康的；well 作为形容词时，指身体好。

因此，正确答案是D。

question_boxs.description: 阅读下列短文，根据短文内容，从短文后各题所给的选项中，选择最佳选项。

content.content:
Yang: Good morning, Betty!

Betty: Good morning, Yang!

Yang: How are you this morning?

Betty: Very well. Thank you.

Yang: Do you know Rose, a new student in Class 3 Grade 7?

Betty: Yes.

Yang: Can you tell me something about her?

Betty: Sure. We're in the same class. I know her very well. She is from England. She speaks English very well. She can speak Chinese, too.

Yang: Do you know her mother?

Betty: Yes, I do. Her mother is an English teacher in our school. She gives us English class every day. She loves Chinese students very much. She is a good teacher. We all love her. It's time to have class. I must go now. Bye!

Yang: Bye!

subContents.content: Rose isn't _____.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：She is from England. 她来自英国。此处“她”指的是Rose，所以Rose 不是美国人。

因此，正确答案是D。

subContents.content: Betty's English teacher _____.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：Her mother is an English teacher in our school. She gives us English class every day. 她妈妈是我们学校的英语老师。她每天给我们上英语课。这是Betty 说的话，“她妈妈”指的是Rose 的妈妈，所以Betty 的英语老师是Rose 的妈妈。

因此，正确答案是A。

subContents.content: What do we know from the passage?

options.option: Rose and Betty are in different classes.
Rose is in the same class with Yang.
Rose is in the same class with Betty.
Rose's mother is the English teacher of Rose, Yang and Betty.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：We're in the same class.我们在同一个班级。此处“我们”指的是Betty 和Rose。

因此，正确答案是C。

subContents.content: Yang _____.

options.option: wants to know about Rose's family

analysisList.text:
此题是推理判断题。答案出处：Do you know Rose, a new student in Class 3 Grade 7? 你认识Rose，七年级三班的一名新生吗？Can you tell me something about her? 你能告诉我关于她的事情吗？Do you know her mother? 你认识她妈妈吗？根据Yang 问的这三个问题可知他想了解Rose 的家庭情况。

因此，正确答案是D。

subContents.content: The dialogue (对话) happens (发生) _____.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：Good morning. Betty! Betty ，早上好！Good morning, Yang!Yang，早上好！根据对话开头两人互问早上好，可推知答案。

因此，正确答案是B。

question_boxs.description: 阅读下列短文，根据短文内容，从短文后各题所给的选项中，选择最佳选项。

content.content:
Hello! I'm Jack, Jack Smith. I'm twelve. I have a sister. Her name is Mary Smith. She is ten now.My first name is Bill, and my last name is Green. You can call me Bill or Bill Green. But you can't call me Green Bill.
Hi! I am Zhang Mingming. Mingming is my given name and Zhang is my family name. I am a Chinese boy, so my name is different from the name of an English boy.Hello! My name is Grace Brown. I am thirteen years old. I have a sister. Her name is Helen. She is thirteen, too. We are twins.

subContents.content: Mary Smith is _____.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：I have a sister. Her name is Mary Smith. 我有一个妹妹。她的名字是Mary Smith。

因此，正确答案是B。

subContents.content: The name "_____" is different from the other (其他的) names.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：I am Zhang Mingming. Mingming is my given name and Zhang is my family name. I am a Chinese boy, so my name is different from the name of an English boy. 我是Zhang Mingming。Mingming是我的名，而Zhang是我的姓。我是一个中国男孩，所以我的名字与英国男孩的名字不同。

因此，正确答案是B。

subContents.content: _____ is Helen's last name.

analysisList.text:
此题是推理判断题。答案出处：My name is Grace Brown. I have a sister. Her name is Helen. 我的名字是Grace Brown。我有一个妹妹。她的名字是Helen。由此可推出Brown是Helen的姓氏。

因此，正确答案是A。

subContents.content: The name "_____" is a wrong (错误的) one.

analysisList.text:
此题是细节理解题。答案出处：I'm Jack, Jack Smith. 我是Jack，Jack Smith。

因此，正确答案是C。

subContents.content: The word "twins" means "_____" in Chinese.

analysisList.text:
此题是词义猜测题。答案出处：I am thirteen years old. I have a sister. She is thirteen, too. We are twins. 我13岁。我有一个妹妹。她也13岁。我们是双胞胎。

因此，正确答案是C。

subContents.content:
假设你是Lucy，请以“I”为题，写一篇50词左右的英语小短文。

_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

answers.answer:
I

My name is Lucy. I'm 12 years old. I come from China. I'm short and thin. I have short hair. I study in No. 1 Middle School. My teachers are very friendly. I like them. I have a good family. My parents love me and I love them.

analysisList.text:
好单词：

  1. name 名字；

  2. short 短的；

  3. teacher 老师；

  4. friendly 友好的；

  5. family 家庭；

好短语：

  1. come from 来自；

  2. Middle School 中学；

  3. be friendly 友好，友善

好句子：

  1. I come from China. 我来自中国。

  2. I have short hair. 我留着短发。

  3. My parents love me and I love them. 我父母爱我，而我也爱他们。

answerList:

My name is Lucy. I'm 12 years old. I come from China. I'm short and thin. I have short hair. I study in No. 1 Middle School. My teachers are very friendly. I like them. I have a good family. My parents love me and I love them.
